DOC.brief_summary: Women with pelvic floor prolapse who underwent surgery with mesh will be enrolled. The investigators will compare data from the chart, telephone interviews and physical examinations between those who underwent mesh placement to those who underwent placement of PIVS.
DOC.brief_title: Treatment of Pelvic Organ Prolapse by PIVS Versus Surgeon Cut Mesh
DOC.criteria: Women who underwent surgery for pelvic floor prolapse Women who did not have surgery for pelvic floor prolapse.
